### **Java Program: Download Image, Apply Filter, Save to Disk**

```java
import java.awt.image.BufferedImage;
import java.awt.image.Kernel;
import java.awt.image.ConvolveOp;
import java.awt.image.EllipseKernel;
import java.awt.image.Filters;
import java.io.*;
import java.net.URL;
